|     Use Case ID         |     UC009                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |   |   |   |   |   |
|-------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Use Case Name       |     Admin add new food item to the list                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Created By          |     Mr.ABC               Last   Updated By                4th   May 2020                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Date Created        |     1 May 2019       Last   Revision By                 1st   May 2020                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Actors              |     Admin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Pre Conditions      |     Internet Connectivity     
                                Browser Compatibility     
                                Admin should be logged in to the system.    
                                Admin should have rights to add products.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Post Conditions     |     A new food item will be added successfully.     
                                Food list will be updated.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Basic Flow          |     Admin access the system and go to the food item list.     
                                System has the option to add new food item for admin login.     
                                Admin selects the option to add new food item into the list.     
                                Admin fills the information.     
                                The system validates the information.     
                                If right then the system adds that new food item into the   product list.     
                                The product list gets updated.  
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Alternate Flow      |     If the admin enters wrong details, then the system will not add the product to the list.     
                                If admin does not fill the mandatory fields then food item will not be added to the food item list.                                                                                                                                                                                  
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Exceptional Flow    |     If the user encounters any technical errors while filling the product details or while logging in to the system.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Assumptions         |     Manufacturer has knowledge of adding product to the list and also how to use the system.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Constraints         |     username cannot be name(It should be email id)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Dependencies        |     None                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Input & Output      |     Input-> tracking ID     
                                Output-> place where the product is will be displayed                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Business Rule       |     Once the order is processed , make the tracking information   available to the user                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |  



