|---------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Use Case   Name       |     Delivery   Boy picks up food from restaurant                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Created By            |     Mr.ABC               Last Updated By                4th May 2020                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Date   Created        |     1 May 2019       Last Revision By                 1st May 2020                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Actors                |     Delivery   Boy                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Pre Conditions        |     Internet Connectivity     
                                  Browser Compatibility     
                                  Delivery Boy should be logged in to the system.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Post   Conditions     |     Food will   be delivered to the customer                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Basic Flow            |     The delivery boy receives a notification or assignment to pick up food from a specific restaurant.   
                                  Delivery boy arrives at the restaurant location within the specified time window.     
                                  Delivery boy identifies himself to the restaurant staff and   provides necessary verification or credentials if required.     
                                  The restaurant staff confirms the order details and hands   over the packed food to the delivery boy.     
                                  Delivery boy checks the received items against the order details to ensure accuracy.     
                                  Once satisfied with the order, the delivery boy securely packs the food for transportation, ensuring it remains fresh and intact.     
                                  Delivery boy leaves the restaurant premises with the food.     
                                  Delivery boy transports the food to the designated delivery address while following the specified route.   
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Alternate Flow      |     If the Delivery Boy enters wrong details, then the system will not validate him                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Exceptional Flow    |     If there are any issues in the order (e.g., missing items,   wrong items) 
                                  The delivery boy notifies the restaurant staff, and they   rectify the issue before proceeding.     
                                  If the food packaging is found to be damaged or compromised, the delivery boy informs the restaurant staff, and they provide a replacement or repackage the food appropriately.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Assumptions         |     Delivery   boy has the knowledge of how to use the system.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Constraints         |     username cannot be name(It should be email id)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Dependencies          |     None                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Input &   Output      |     Input->   tracking ID    
                                  Output->   place where the product is will be displayed                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Business   Rule       |     Once the   order is processed , make the tracking information available to the Admin                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



