|-------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Use Case Name       |     Delivery Updates                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Created By          |     Mr.ABC               Last   Updated By                4th   May 2020                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Date Created        |     1 May 2019       Last   Revision By                 1st   May 2020                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Actors              |     Delivery Boy
                                Customer                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Pre Conditions      |     Internet Connectivity     
                                Browser Compatibility     
                                Delivery Boy should be logged in to the system.    
                                Delivery order is placed and assigned to the delivery boy.     
                                The delivery boy has necessary equipment.     
                                The customers contact information and address is available to   the delivery boy.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Post Conditions     |     The delivery status is updated in the system.     
                                The customer receives the real time updates from the system.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Basic Flow          |     The delivery boy receives a notification or assignment to pick   up food from a specific restaurant.     
                                Delivery boy arrives at the restaurant location within the   specified time window.     
                                Delivery boy identifies himself to the restaurant staff and provides necessary verification or credentials if required.     
                                The restaurant staff confirms the order details and hands over the packed food to the delivery boy.     
                                Delivery boy checks the received items against the order details to ensure accuracy.     
                                Once satisfied with the order, the delivery boy securely packs the food for transportation, ensuring it remains fresh and intact.     
                                Delivery boy leaves the restaurant premises with the food.     
                                Delivery boy starts delivery route.     
                                Delivery boy arrives at the customers location.     
                                Delivery boy hands over the order to the customer.     
                                He updates the status in the system.    
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Alternate Flow      |     If there is unexpected delay during the delivery, the delivery driver updates the status in the system.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |   |   |   |   |   |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Exceptional Flow    |     If there are any issues in the order (e.g., missing items, wrong items), the delivery boy notifies the restaurant staff, and they rectify the issue before proceeding.    
                                If the food packaging is found to be damaged or compromised, the delivery boy informs the restaurant staff, and they provide a replacement or repackage the food appropriately.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |   |   |   |   |   |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Assumptions         |     Delivery boy has the knowledge of how to use the system.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |   |   |   |   |   |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Constraints         |     The delivery updates must be accurate.     
                                The delivery updates must be provided on time.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |   |   |   |   |   |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Dependencies        |     Availability of GPS.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |   |   |   |   |   |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Input & Output      |     Input-> tracking ID, delivery details, customer information    
                                Output-> notification gone to the customer.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Business Rule       |     Delivery updates should be provided time to time in order to ensure transparency.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |   |   |   |   |   |

