                                Browser Compatibility     
                                The customer has successfully placed the order.     
                                The customer has provided valid email address during ordering   process.                                                                                                                                                                    |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Post Conditions     |     The customer receives email confirmation of the ordered food.     
                                The system records the order and send relevant details to the kitchen for preparation.                                                                                                                                                                                          |   |   |   |   |   |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Basic Flow          |     After placing the order, the restaurant system generates an order confirmation email.     
                                The email includes details such   as order items, quantity, total amount, estimated delivery time, and contact information.     
                                The email is sent to the   customer's provided email address.      
                                The customer receives the email   confirmation.    
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Alternate Flow      |     If the customer does not receive the confirmation email within a reasonable timeframe, they may check their spam or junk folder.      
                                If not found, they can contact customer support for assistance.                                                                                                                                        
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Exceptional Flow    |     If there are technical issues with the email service provider or the restaurant system, the email confirmation may be delayed or not sent at all.     
                                the customer may be informed through alternative channels, such as a notification on the restaurant's website or app.                                                               
